  "texts": [
    "Within the humanities, working with digitised (primary) source material is no longer a novelty.",
    "Due to both large and small projects over recent years, an increasing number of digital sources have become available.",
    "Most of these projects have been realised and enriched with Automatic Text Recognition (ATR, machine learning-based text recognition for print and handwriting) techniques.",
    "Although the resulting data sets of machine-readable texts are immensely promising for the humanities, these developments also inevitably challenge existing disciplinary practices.",
    "This paper revolves around several challenges tied to preparing and publishing ATR results."
  ],
